data.description: Welcome Home to Charming Colonial Elegance!  PRICE REDUCED!!!!  Nestled on a spacious 0.37-acre lot, this meticulously maintained residence boasts classic colonial style across two inviting house levels. Your journey begins with a convenient garage and a well-manicured driveway, offering ample parking for residents and guests alike.  Step inside to discover a home that has been recently painted, radiating a fresh and welcoming ambiance throughout. The thoughtful design includes two and a half baths, complete with a relaxing tub for moments of indulgence and rejuvenation.  With attention to detail evident in every corner, this property seamlessly blends modern comfort with timeless charm. Whether you're enjoying the warmth of the fireplace or entertaining in the open-concept living spaces, this home is designed for both relaxation and social gatherings.  Take advantage of the expansive backyard, providing a private oasis for outdoor activities or potential landscaping dreams. The generous lot size ensures a sense of space and privacy, creating a perfect retreat from the hustle and bustle of daily life.  This residence is not just a house; it's a lifestyle. Embrace the convenience of a thoughtfully designed layout, the tranquility of a sizable backyard, and the joy of calling this colonial gem your home. Schedule you're showing today and experience the allure of this property firsthand.
